settings?
	There are many different settings

	Typically, settings refers to puppet main settings

	represented by puppet.conf

	can typically be set on command line as part of various puppet commands

	settings that require complex data structure are stored in separate files

		only simple props can be stored in puppet.conf


	main settings

	location

		root
		/etc/puppetlabs/puppet

		non-root
		~/.puppetlabs/etc/puppet

